      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 47,
      "message": "Remove properties centralized class (Prop) add sonar blocker error like :\nhttps://sonarcloud.io/project/issues?id=onap_dmaap-messagerouter-dmaapclient&issues=AXkALsra1aqw2hxRNQ68&open=AXkALsra1aqw2hxRNQ68\n\nSome global variable have the same name that properties name (but in upper case). So to make something unified I added PROP all over.\n\nSorry to insist, but have a single class with all properties constant is for me the best solution. (and avoid a lot of duplication)",
      "author": {
